
devpi-installer (Ubuntu)
========================

Create a devpi-server instance and configure supervisord to manage it.

devpi
-----

devpi-server is a caching PyPi proxy, it makes Python package installation
more reliable and much faster.


Usage
-----

Clone source::

    $ git clone git@github.com:averagehuman/devpi-installer.git

In the source directory run the ``install`` make target::

    $ cd devpi-installer
    $ sudo make install

Start the server with::

    $ supervisorctl reread
    $ supervisorctl update


